The '''Number Five External Hard Dock''' was a dock onboard the ''[[Glorious]]''. [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] convinced [[Lieutenant/Legends|Lieutenant]] [[Ijix Harona]] to let him dock the [[Lady Luck/Legends|''Lady Luck'']] there after mentioning that after talking with [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Ejagga Pakkpekatt]], he would ask him to conduct a review of the bridge procedures and staff, and find out why a flag officer and the Fleet Operations delegation to the mission were kept waiting while the officer of the day, Harona, was thumbing through a regulation manual.

